This project includes Lean 4 formalizations of a sublogarithmic bound for
lattice points on short circular arcs, together with supporting Gaussian integer,
determinant, modular collision, Chebyshev interval, and prime descent machinery.

This project includes code adapted from the PrimeNumberTheoremAnd project
(https://github.com/AlexKontorovich/PrimeNumberTheoremAnd), licensed under the
Apache License 2.0.  See GaussianChain/MertensFirst.lean, adapted from
PrimeNumberTheoremAnd/IEANTN/Mertens.lean.
